          {
            "title": "Cours 11 _ Gammapathies monoclonales",
            "lines": [
              "RT : Rihème Saidane / Rania Saidane RL : Ines HAMDI",
              "UE 6 – Hématologie",
              "Dr Lazarian Grégory– 12/03/2026 – 13h45 - 15h15",
